cluded in “liabilities”. The word “outstanding” is omitted as unnecessary. The words “as provided by” are substituted for “in accordance with the determination of” to eliminate unnecessary words. The words “and all Federal and States laws applicable thereto” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
